      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:63:8",
      "text": [
        " مَنْ أَقَرَّ بِوَلَدٍ ثُمَّ نَفَاهُ جُلِدَ الْحَدَّ وَ أُلْزِمَ الْوَلَدَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Al Nowfaly, from Al Sakuny, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> that Amir Al-Momineen<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The one who confesses with (ownership of) a child, then denies it, would be whipped the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>), and the child would be enforced upon him’."
        ]
      }
